title: Changed public access around Canobolas State Forest (Forestry Corporation of NSW)
text: ( Source : Forestry Corporation of NSW ) 19 Oct 2015 - Jacinta Healy Locals are being reminded to pay attention to road closures and warning signs when visiting Canobolas State Forest during timber harvesting operations starting in November
